  m_text: 'This game is a reimagination of the Mad Game jam, where instead of a fun
    and welcoming experience, jammers face an  evil staff team that wishes to keep
    them trapped in order to make games for their own entertainment.


    To escape,
    you must become ping pong master, and earn the respect of the janitor, former
    world champion, and acquire the key to the front door.'
